a Star Wars guy.

00:49:44.710 --> 00:49:46.810
Each of them showed
a higher level

00:49:46.810 --> 00:49:50.130
of expressive and receptive
speech and connection

00:49:50.130 --> 00:49:54.810
than basically the parents had
ever seen on the first usage.

00:49:54.810 --> 00:49:56.030
It's crazy.

