concert my whole life.

00:57:42.220 --> 00:57:44.940
It's so exciting to think
about content living

00:57:44.940 --> 00:57:47.770
more fully and deeply
in people's lives

00:57:47.770 --> 00:57:50.610
where they actually live.

00:57:50.610 --> 00:57:54.140
I mean, that's the dream, for
all available knowledge that's

00:57:54.140 --> 00:57:57.270
now sitting on a PDA.

00:57:57.270 --> 00:58:00.900
And these kids, I think, are
going to lead that charge.

00:58:00.900 --> 00:58:03.220
That's the most
exciting part about it.

